{"tid":2183314,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蓬佩奧：特朗普或於數周內公布限制中國學生赴美細節","createTime":"2020-09-01T00:53:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T11:09:37.000Z","uid":39464,"like":703,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"069d4c05f726a53a9b02bcd765d3d299bd03ea28","tid":2183314,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T00:53:11.000Z","msg":"美國國務卿蓬佩奧表示，總統特朗普正認真考慮限制中國留學生或研究人員到美國，可能在未來數星期或數個月，會公布細節。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧接受美國一個電台訪問時表示，並非所有到美國的中國學生都是為中國共產黨工作，不應被視為間諜，但中共一直密切他們，確保他們聽命於中共，令這些學生感到很大壓力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547126-20200901.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547126-20200901.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7v1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=71740dd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547126-20200901.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=98d2a61e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547126-20200901.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"8e145846e1694a726c548a7879c1b7f3b4f80634","tid":2183314,"uid":237517,"like":64,"dislike":3,"score":61,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T00:53:50.000Z","msg":"仲數周<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50bbe79d0b353d249dc12757cb68192fe4694f93","tid":2183314,"uid":303466,"like":247,"dislike":2,"score":245,"citedBy":19,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T00:56:38.000Z","msg":"即係香港學生都冇得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af024bb79abfbacdeadd56aaf587abb063335e5f","tid":2183314,"uid":184581,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T00:59:10.000Z","msg":"原來仲未做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543f08c94a2f58b327bbdec253264b788c12dc9e","tid":2183314,"uid":370972,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"quote":{"pid":"50bbe79d0b353d249dc12757cb6